Transparency International releases its Corruption Perception Index showing Denmark, New Zealand and Singapore as the least corrupt nations and Somalia as the most corrupt. (CNN)The Republican and Democratic party caucuses in the United States House of Representatives hold leadership elections. Nancy Pelosi of the Democrats is elected as Minority Leader when the new House sits in January with John Boehner to become Speaker of the United States House of Representatives. (CNN), (MSNBC), (CNN)